                        <interp inst="t18501021-name-1053" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN KELLY</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-sergeant, P</hi> 22). I received these two shillings from Baker.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18501021-name-1054" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18501021-name-1054" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18501021-name-1054" type="surname" value="WEBSTER"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18501021-name-1054" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM WEBSTER</persName>
                  </hi>. This half-crown and these two shillings are counterfeit.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I had no idea it was bad money.</p>
